The tests below are all fine:
 - IsObjectClass = (GetSuperclass() == nullptr)
 - IsInterface - from access flags
 - IsArrayClass - (GetComponentType() == nullptr)
 - IsAssignableFrom - uses IsSubClass and Implements, both should be okay

Either way, testing for IsResolved, as we found some time ago, is non-deterministic. So we should record these dependencies.

